products.title: Black Seamless No Show Cheeky Briefs x2
products.body_html:
LOVE SEAMLESS...

Meet our first fully Seamless Cheeky Briefs.

The No Show Cheeky Briefs are the perfect style to team under your Lounge Leggings or any outfit that requires the perfect no show underwear for a seamless fit and feel.

Our No Show style is simple and chic. Your purchase will include a pack of 2.

PRODUCT DETAILS

Nathalya wears: Small Cheeky Briefs

  • 74% polyamide and 26% spandex
  • subtle Lounge underwear logo branding on the hipline
  • fully seamless design
  • all black construction
